{"tid":2345824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣國防部發布年終影片：無畏無懼 守護家園","createTime":"2020-12-29T23:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T00:10:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c258cb6a3491609c7efe592b63af68ed85321173","tid":2345824,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T23:59:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">無畏無懼 守護家園</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/12/30 05:30<br />\n明天為2020年最後一天，雖然國軍今年肇生數起事故，致使故參謀總長沈一鳴等人離世，但國防部昨日發布一支影片，展示包括黑鷹直升機、OH-58D直升機、F-16戰機、陸戰隊突擊艇等多項軍備，藉由畫面深刻表達官兵用性命拚搏，及在演訓中展現無所畏懼的勇氣。<span class=\"red\">國防部表示，盼以此片紀念今年以身殉職的國軍將士。\b</span>（圖：擷取自「國防部發言人」臉書，文：記者涂鉅旻）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MilitarySpokesman/videos/485378139097566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMilitarySpokesman%2Fvideos%2F485378139097566&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c456b776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MilitarySpokesman/videos/485378139097566</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1422251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1422251&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=476cb4a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1422251&h=1d402718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1422251</a>"},{"pid":"8cf2c79ec5fe8bd25395d097d967ca832ad4dd4b","tid":2345824,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f0e1bbfe486b52a1a548aeacea58aba39a14ea8","tid":2345824,"uid":49859,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:01:47.000Z","msg":"人地嘅守護家園打外敵<br />\n香港嘅「守護家園」打市民"},{"pid":"4e56ff0a6c78b11e343f248ab528e1c5b755b47f","tid":2345824,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,